  "texts": [
    "Consequently, research on AI methods aims to address how to establish a correspondence between the drug and the target.",
    "Present research tackles this issue in two main approaches.",
    "Firstly, it explores the existence of a correlation between the drug and the target and treats the relationship as a \"0/1\" problem.",
    "This classification problem can be resolved through binary classification or by assigning a candidate ranking.",
    "Secondly, it utilizes the affinity coefficient relationship between the drug and the target to evaluate and normalize their association as a \"0/1\" problem."
  ],
